b1b5761071fdf2504ff32ea36e2fd","tid":2478373,"uid":3860,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"81966f1a00bfc55f0c29e0f51ce0f83abe1eb8a3","tid":2478373,"uid":30552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fus-politics%2Fdhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=c40f3517\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOwSwHU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOwSwHU.png&h=3423071c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上係Congress已經撥咗錢去呢個project, 所以個project就要完成，除非有特別原因或者總統反對。牆都起到差唔多用得，唔通就咁擺喺度唔埋埋尾？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"你UP 乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n拜登一直反對起牆，而家佢咪係你講既「總統反對」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌左侵起牆咁耐，拎晒道德光環，而家自己做總統有權力取消反而繼續?<br />\n<br />\n咁你都覺得OK? 冇野呀話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.factcheck.org/2020/12/trumps-border-wall-where-does-it-stand/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factcheck.org%2F2020%2F12%2Ftrumps-border-wall-where-does-it-stand%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=4fbfafe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factcheck.org/2020/12/trumps-border-wall-where-does-it-stand/</a><br />\n其實一開始反對Trump起牆係因為佢2016 開始競選嗰時嘅共和黨platform 係話成個南邊都要有border wall (即係差唔多兩千里）但係Trump 自己講嘅就變成要起1000里。之後佢成日改個數，講過900,800,700,500. 但係其實本身個邊境都有六百幾里嘅border barriers. 到而家睇返佢好似起咗總共四百幾里，但係當中只有四五十里係新嘅，其他都只係將舊嘅barrier維修。係佢講到咁浮誇，又話要1000里（咁撚多要好多錢，用咁多錢去起牆但係啲人主要係飛過嚟唔走，起牆對呢啲逾期居留無用，而且無乜可能起咁多，因為好多地都係私人嘅），又話要墨西哥埋單（人地睬你都on9)，又話要用嚟杜絕偷渡，啲人先唔贊成之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n拜登做senator同VP 嗰陣都有贊成過起border barrier, 本身邊境某啲位都已經有。佢競選時係話過當選後唔起嘅，但係而家起，主要係埋咗trump啲牆嘅尾啫，唔通擺咗咁多錢落去就由佢爛尾？我上個post條link有哂件事嘅details, 如果你係要執住「總之佢話過唔起架，而家又起喎！」嚟講，咁就係啦，唔阻你地圍爐"}]}